A linked list can be reversed either iteratively or recursively. Could you implement both?
思路&题解
public ListNode reverseList(ListNode head) {
    ListNode pre = null;
    ListNode current = head;
    while(current!=null){
        ListNode next = current.next;
        current.next = pre;
        pre = current;
        current = next;
    }
    return pre;
}

